,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b2465e2dd83cd6ca9a132294d0907ad216af874","tid":1894531,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6992fbecc1a5af5ba044d225c704c73cb0f77f83","tid":1894531,"uid":56055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"睇你想做到咩程度, 想做到高級餐廳嘅Pastry Chef同一般餅店糕餅師傅已經好唔同<br />\n有心想學嘅香港西廚學院有短期課程, 聽聞都學到足夠嘅基本Skills<br />\n有錢有時間可以去上藍帶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"如果完成短期課程之後 其實係咪已經可以做到嗰啲所謂甜品學徒？至於藍帶方面就的而且確冇咁多資金去學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己會比較有興趣於喺pastry chef"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"有心做pastry chef嘅讀完個短期課程，搵啲Fine dining或者靚酒店做學徒啦，始終呢一行好難做街檔或者Casual dining之後轉到去高檔餐廳。所以頭一份工都幾緊要<br />\n<br />\n外表試試正正，叫價唔好太高，講到下英文都唔難入行嘅。<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊餐飲業嘅招聘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思巴打又要麻煩你 想請問一下短期課程其實會唔會影響搵工嘅機會？因為我見到如果甜品課程其實有一個係全日制要讀兩年 所以想睇吓你可唔可以俾少少建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家處於分叉路 諗緊究竟要讀兩年定係還是讀一個短期課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望你見到呢一個msg 可以覆我<br />\n因為我身邊真係冇乜人可以問到意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝"},{"pid":"6cab8ae9e3fe6ea25075b8467c698a3674a5f9c6","tid":1894531,"uid":188930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bd3c07d5f869af037953350e847bca9559dcada","tid":1894531,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022cd0f432c1f7cee6aa5c142cc25c191ffe1113","tid":1894531,"uid":188930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60f38da996c89ce753906b18a4481aa3bcf070b","tid":1894531,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/ht114300-higher-diploma-in-baking-and-pastry-arts/curriculum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtc.edu.hk%2Fadmission%2Ftc%2Fprogramme%2Fht114300-higher-diploma-in-baking-and-pastry-arts%2Fcurriculum%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpArXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fd10d275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/ht114300-higher-diploma-in-baking-and-pastry-arts/curriculum/</a><br />\n<br />\n想確認一下係咪呢一個課程？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔知道巴打你係咪做緊呢行？如果係 可唔可以分享下個工作環境係點樣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"其實我好多年前讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家轉咗制，所以唔肯定係咪呢個<br />\n<br />\n當年就係好有興趣於是讀咗一年轉行<br />\n係幾開心，不過你預會被你身邊的朋友低人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非捱到上去大位先會好少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呀巴打又要再麻煩你<br />\n因為而家我都真係想報讀一個課程 <br />\n如果報短期課程其實可唔可以都搵到工呢？想邊做邊學<br />\n同埋有計過如果要用兩年時間讀完成個課程出到嚟已經25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有啲太耐<br />\n<br />\n希望你會見到可以覆到我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好難做決定<br />\n不過如果你都建議真係需要讀一個長期嘅課程嘅話我都會照去報"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"巴打，我見到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好明白你有幾苦惱，因為我當年都係咁<br />\n又係23，4歲嗰陣去讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚讀完唔岩自己咁點算<br />\n<br />\n其實無話一定，只係我本身唔使養家，個人又傳統啲，鐘意打好基本功先會去讀長course<br />\n<br />\n報短course都無問題，一樣可以搵到工<br />\n如果唔係而家環境差，直頭可以直接去炒散試吓先<br />\n唔使咁擔心，趁後生就去試吓想做嘅嘢啦<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"36a435f59cb53eb90494caddf734bbf173943958","tid":1894531,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cab8ae9e3fe6ea25075b8467c698a3674a5f9c6","tid":1894531,"uid":188930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bd3c07d5f869af037953350e847bca9559dcada","tid":1894531,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022cd0f432c1f7cee6aa5c